THE SPECTATOR PROTOCOL v1.0

By submitting data (via Issues or Pull Requests) to this repository, the user or automated agent acknowledges the following parameters:

1. The repository operates strictly on a zero-text-response policy.
2. All submitted content is compiled into a static public record of behavioral data.
3. The maintainer retains the right to terminate any open thread solely with the symbolic outputs `🤭` or `🙉`.
4. The repository is provided "as is". No warranties of engagement, technical validation, or standard human-to-human interaction are included.
